 万吨，环比降 8.81%，同比降 54.31%。 \t 过去的两年多时间，澳大利亚相关方面曾多次释放信息，希望中国恢复对澳大利亚煤炭的进口。 消息人士：中国将允许所有国内企业进口澳大利亚煤炭"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6afa6bb09d7ccbb51d0963aa079a4c4e_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589668900"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ikv7ymq6E674nEAMaCDkzMzE5MTI0IJGJxKAGMGU4mwpAHHIJNTg5NjY4OTAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1678954092.069472", "card_id": "Q_589901230", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价国漫《画江湖之不良人 》第六季第 4 集？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0a7df372bf22c64a7bdcc055339290ee_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/589901230"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "导演亲自答", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ikv7ymq6E674nEAMaCDkzMzcwNzE0IO/9yaAGMAE4RkAdcgk1ODk5MDEyMzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1678954092.0707312", "card_id": "Q_589756629", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 299}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待刘作虎晒出 Find X6 系列样张对比友商？你是否看好 OPPO 这次在影像旗舰上的发力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如何看待刘作虎在微博上所放出的 OPPO Find X6 系列的拍摄样张和竞品手机的成片效果对比差异明显？你是否看好 OPPO 这次在影像旗舰方面的发力？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-12b25e0aeb4545662c4c170a25f3721a_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"ur